description: Prawns and avocados are the perfect classic pairing in this fresh and vibrant taco recipe that's ready in 3 steps. Serve with extra salsa on the side.
name: Prawn & Avocado Tacos Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat a large frying pan over medium heat. Add prawns and cook for 1 minute each side or until cooked through. Divide prawn mixture among tortillas. Top with avocado and a little salsa. Serve.
